info.author: David Cramer
info.description:
# ds-cli

This is a command line interface to [DS](https://github.com/getsentry/ds).

```bash
$ ds-cli deploy example
Created new Task with ID = 1

$ ds-cli tail -f 1
(waiting for output..)
# ...
```
